      "span_text": "This representation is different from Gaussian Mixture Models used for density estimation with Expectation-Maximization techniques  : while Expectation-Maximization gives higher values where the density of samples is higher, our RBF decomposition interpolates values stored at arbitrarily scattered sample points.",
